        <img src={{cdn}}/img/browse.blue.svg alt='DLx data explorer logo'>
        <p>Browse public data in the DLx crosslinguistic database. Search for typological patterns. Collect statistics on language data.</p>
      </a>
    </section> --}}

    <a class="twitter-timeline" data-theme="light" href="https://twitter.com/digitalling">Tweets by digitalling</a>

  </div>

</main>

